{{see|Filter}}
==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-filter.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪltə(r)|-ɪltə(r)]]
* fihl'tr

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A device which [[separate]]s a [[suspended]], [[dissolved]], or [[particulate]] matter from a fluid, solution, or other [[substance]]; any device that separates one substance from another.
# [[Electronics]] or [[software]] that separate unwanted [[signal]] (for example [[noise]]) from wanted signal or that [[attenuates]] selected [[frequencies]].
# Any [[item]], [[mechanism]], [[device]] or [[procedure]] that acts to [[separate]] or [[isolate]].
# A device that changes [[light]] so that only one type of light (IE [[ultraviolet]]) passes through it.
#:''He ran an email '''filter''' to catch the junk mail.''

